'''Jurrinex6''' was a [[hive virus]] developed by biological [[Terrorist/Legends|terrorists]] at the height of the [[New Order/Legends|New Order]].

In the past four centuries before the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], the lethal Jurrinex6 and [[Jurr-5]] hive viruses were responsible for over 100 million [[Death/Legends|deaths]].

The [[kalaide]]s of the planet [[Cols/Legends|Cols]] produced [[masrizeen]], the basis for the first effective antidote against these two hive viruses.

